insert into venue values (NULL,'Alon Zakaim Fine Art strives to be a leader in Impressionist, Modern and Contemporary art. Dealing in a wide range of work, the gallery exhibits a distinguished collection of high quality paintings and sculptures. The gallery aims to provide a knowledgeable, efficient and accessible service to all their clients.

