insert into venue values (NULL,'arebyte gallery is a cross disciplinary  space in East London working mainly in Performance and New-Media arts researching the relationship between the body,  technology and human experience. We work with local and international artists on-site and on-line, promoting new and innovative means of engaging the public and facilitating participation.
 
