insert into venue values (NULL,'Founded in October 2005 by Charlie Phillips, previously founding director of Haunch of Venison, and Laura Lopes, Eleven is committed to exhibiting the best of international contemporary art by both established and emerging artists. Susannah Haworth Dunn is the gallery manager.

