insert into venue values (NULL,'Evelyn Yard, London, opened with its first exhibition in June 2014 and has since programmed a series of exhibitions by artists, writers and performers. We work with an international group of artists who are at the start of their careers or have not been exhibited in London before. We actively promote each of the artists and have a particular focus on placing works within established and institutional collections, as well as introducing a younger set of collectors to artists from their own generation. We have a particular focus on language and ideas of production and the image in the digital age.','Evelyn Yard',2,CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,'Evelyn Yard W1T 1HN London',NULL,0,51.5168265,'Evelyn Yard W1T 1HN London',-0.13307420000001,'Wednesday - Saturday : 11:00 - 18:00',CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,'www.evelynyard.com');
insert into venue values (NULL,'Eykyn Maclean is a private gallery based in New York and London, specializing in museum quality Impressionist and 20th century European and American Art.
 
