insert into venue values (NULL,'Ever since she can remember Francesca dreamed of opening her own contemporary art gallery. In pursuit of this dream she read History of Art at Reading University and graduated with a First Class Honors degree. Francesca opened her first art gallery in 2001 whilst completing her Master’s degree.

