insert into venue values (NULL,'Heathwall Limited trading as Hay Hill Gallery is situated in the prestigious Marylebone district of the City of Westminster in London. This stunning glass fronted gallery looking over Baker Street and Blandford Street specialises in contemporary and modern arts and presents an ever-changing collection of sculptures and paintings by a number of internationally recognised artists. The gallery works mostly in a primary market.

