insert into venue values (NULL,'Herrick Gallery was founded in Shoreditch in 2012. Drawing inspiration from part domestic, part public gallery spaces like Kettle\'s Yard and the Artists\' House, Roche Court. The small east London gallery space proved to be a great success with a busy programme of solo & group exhibitions, launches and external events. In 2015 Herrick Gallery launched in Mayfair in newly refurbished premises over three floors on Piccadilly with views across Green Park. The gallery collaborates with established artists as well as discovering, nurturing and promoting emerging artists and designers whose work has a rigorous intellectual enquiry, dedication to their craft, honesty, sensitivity and beauty. The gallery also hosts a series of talks and events as part of the exhibition programme.','Herrick Gallery',2,CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,'93 Piccadilly W1J 7NQ London',NULL,0,51.5063721,'93 Piccadilly W1J 7NQ London',-0.149009500000034,'Tuesday - Saturday : 11:00 - 18:00, Monday : by appointment',CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,'www.herrickgallery.com');
