insert into venue values (NULL,'Lawrence Alkin Gallery is an independently run, commercial art gallery located in the centre of London. Operating from our split-level boutique space that was once TomTom and, until recently, artrepublic Soho, the primary goal for us is to seek to develop the next generation of artists through exciting and different exhibitions, events and exclusive publications from a breadth of talent. Contemporary, urban, street and pop art; we don’t distinguish or discriminate, but embrace and look to display visually engaging exhibitions from a hybrid of artistic disciplines.

