insert into venue values (NULL,'Maddox Arts is a contemporary art gallery founded in 2007 in Mayfair London at 52 Brook\'s Mews. The gallery’s aim is to fosters emerging and mid-career artists from the UK and internationally. Maddox Arts portfolio selection is influenced by architecture, geometric abstraction, constructivism and photography. Sometime is the use of the space, other times It’s the thinking behind the idea, painting, drawing or installation that we cherish. Conceptual art and painting are equally valued. We often use external curators from different backgrounds to give an opportunity to new artists bringing in this way a fresh breath of air to the area','Maddox Arts',2,CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,'52 Brook\'s Mews W1K 4ED London',NULL,0,51.5125622,'52 Brook\'s Mews W1K 4ED London',-0.146565099999975,'Monday - Friday : 10:00 - 18:00, Saturday : 12:00 - 18:00, or by appointment',CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,'www.maddoxarts.com');
