insert into venue values (NULL,'Pump House Gallery is a public contemporary exhibition space housed in a distinctive four story grade II listed Victorian tower in the centre of Battersea Park. Collaboration and participation is at the heart of its programme, working in partnership to bring engaging contemporary art to Wandsworth Borough and beyond. The diverse range of exhibitions are supported by workshops, temporary projects and one-off events that welcome everyone to explore the different ways art can be made, experienced and interpreted.','Pump House Gallery',2,CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,'Battersea Park SW11 4NJ London',NULL,0,51.4789905,'Battersea Park SW11 4NJ London',-0.161823499999969,'Wednesday - Sunday :  11:00 - 16:00',CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,'www.pumphousegallery.org.uk');
