insert into venue values (NULL,'Vigo represents emerging and established international artists, curating shows in both the public and private arenas.  We advise several residencies and enjoy good relations with many Museums and Foundations from the TATE to the British Museum, The Met and the Saatchi Gallery. We source important works for the Levett Collection (Christian Levett) and often help to place them on loan. Recent acquisitions include Ai Wei Wei’s Iron Tree, which we loaned to Yorkshire Sculpture Park for seven years and which formed the nucleus of his show there. We have placed approximately 15 works by our artists in National museums over the last two years as well as a similar number in private museums. ','Vigo Gallery',2,CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,'21 Dering Street W1S 1AL London',NULL,0,51.5142546,'21 Dering Street W1S 1AL London',-0.145545200000015,'Monday – Friday : 10:00 – 18:00, Saturday : 11:00 - 16:00',CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,'www.vigogallery.com');
