insert into venue values (NULL,'Philips Art Gallery opened in 1996 with an exhibition of paintings by a handful of talented graduates from the art schools of England and Scotland. Eighteen years on, twentieth century British and European art figures prominently in gallery exhibitions alongside contemporary painting and photography.

