insert into venue values (NULL,'HANGFIRE is a Bristol based art gallery, specialising in contemporary urban art and graffiti art styles. Our home is the Bedminster area of the city. From this location, we present a solid program of exhibitions and events throughout the year, exhibiting with both emerging and established artists. Formed in 2012 as a pop-up, primarily exhibiting in London and Bristol. With in 2 years of popping up, we decided to opened our first permanent art gallery right here, in Bristol.

