insert into venue values (NULL,'There\'s more to MOSTYN than its reputation as the leading gallery of contemporary art in Wales, UK. MOSTYN is the most friendly and inspiring place to experience art and architecture, to eat, to shop, to meet a friend and to learn or do something new.
 
